            A restaking-powered network where operators run Blueprints — modular service templates that earn fees on every execution.
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="wf-button-row">
          <a href="https://docs.tangle.tools" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="wf-btn-secondary">Explore Docs</a>
          <a href="/stake" class="wf-btn-primary">View Stake</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="wf-video-mask">
        <video
          autoplay
          loop
          muted
          playsinline
          poster="/images/hero/abstract-objects-poster.jpg"
          class="wf-hero-video-poster"
